{"tid":2215333,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"6年情盡！阿蘇哭別巴塞隊友","createTime":"2020-09-24T02:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T10:29:18.000Z","uid":72497,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5c1acb01f0dc90abe442a4eff34596697bb838","tid":2215333,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:30:39.000Z","msg":"蘇亞雷斯在加盟馬德里體育會前，周三最後一次踏足巴塞隆拿訓練場，跟隊友說再見，感動得流下男兒淚。<br />\n<br />\n據西班牙傳媒報道，蘇亞雷斯（Luis Suarez）周三返回巴塞隆拿訓練場，跟一眾合作6年的隊友說再見。「阿蘇」駕車離開時，更被發現用手臂抹眼淚，明顯非常不捨。 由於巴塞跟蘇亞雷斯商討解約時，表明不希望這名33歲烏拉圭國腳免費加盟馬德里體育會，馬體會為簽入心頭好，決定付出400萬歐元轉會費，據報他將與「床單兵團」簽約2年。 <br />\n<br />\n阿蘇2014年以8230萬歐元轉會費，從利物浦加盟巴塞，多年來上陣283場攻入198球，成為球會史上入球王第3位。不過，巴塞經過上季慘淡球季後，今年引入新帥朗奴高文重組，阿蘇立即遭放棄。"},{"pid":"7863087743e8cf6748801c09eaa1ffaeaf974860","tid":2215333,"uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/alexpintanel/status/1308728044035678211?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1308730677857263616%7Ctwgr%5Eshare_3&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Ftalksport.com%2Ffootball%2F763842%2Fluis-suarez-tears-barcelona-atletico-madrid-transfer%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Falexpintanel%2Fstatus%2F1308728044035678211%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1308730677857263616%257Ctwgr%255Eshare_3%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftalksport.com%252Ffootball%252F763842%252Fluis-suarez-tears-barcelona-atletico-madrid-transfer%252F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=20e58e67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Falexpintanel%2Fstatus%2F1308728044035678211%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1308730677857263616%257Ctwgr%255Eshare_3%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftalksport.com%252Ffootball%252F763842%252Fluis-suarez-tears-barcelona-atletico-madrid-transfer%252F&h=55fa02f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/alexpin